26 Sen Floor Amend 1A AM 47 0225
ADOPTED
Senators Jones II of the 22nd and Jackson of the 41st offered the following amendment #1A:
1 Amend the amendment to SB 3 EX (AM 47 0224) by deleting "and" on line 25;
2 By replacing the period on line 27 with a semicolon;
3 By inserting following line 27 the following:
4 (4) One member of the House of Representatives to be appointed by the minority leader
5 of the House of Representatives; and
6 (5) One member of the Senate to be appointed by the minority leader of the Senate.
